tourBios.curYrHigh: Joined PGA TOUR Latinoamérica by claiming medalist honors at the Mazatlan, Mexico Q-School in January. Shot 67-70-66-70 to finish at 15-under and win by one over Mexico's Gerardo Ruiz.
tourBios.carHigh:
2015: Despite finishing T33 at the Argentina Q-School, one spot outside the top-32 who earned status, he went on to make eight starts on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica… His best finish and only top-25 was T17 at the Mazatlán Open on his first start of the season… Made four cuts and finished the year ranked 114th on the Order of Merit.

2014: Missed the cut in all four of his starts on PGA TOUR Canada.
tourBios.personal: Has two siblings, a twin brother Mike and sister Liz... Twitter name is @daverose2
